  "stem": "<p>The table below shows three values of <i>x</i> and their corresponding values of <i>y</i>.</p><table border=\"1\"><tr><th><i>x</i></th><th><i>y</i></th></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>24</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>20</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>16</td></tr></table><p>There is a linear relationship between <i>x</i> and <i>y</i>. Which of the following equations represents this relationship?</p>",
